<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，天气晴朗，阳光灿烂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>四年级学生们去外面收集做美术作品时用的落叶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贝柔老师读了一个有趣的故事，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>说有一只懒大雁为了过冬飞往南方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊几乎把坏小提琴的事情全忘了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33663</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>下一节课是社会研究。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33664</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“昨天，我们讲了目标。” 贝柔老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁记得什么是目标？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45430</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“目标是一个人想要的东西。” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45431</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也是一个人要努力实现的东西。” 奥利维亚说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55149</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对。” 贝柔老师说，“谁能举一个例子？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55150</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你想考试考得好，就得努力学习。” 劳拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60866</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66473</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你想打好棒球，就得多练习。” 拉里说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66474</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71576</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你想要的东西需要花很多钱呢？” 乔伊问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“比如说新鞋！” 奥利维亚说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“或者新滑板。” 卢克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以把它们叫做金钱目标。” 贝柔老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“乔伊，你需要钱吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86404</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。” 乔伊说，“我想演奏曾祖母的小提琴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，琴弦断了，琴桥碎了，琴弓需要修理，全都需要钱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是啊，当你需要钱时，你就得工作。” 贝柔老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我？可是，我太小了，还不能工作。” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有其他的办法可以赚到钱。” 贝柔老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看看周围，发挥你的想象力，想一想！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125477</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“想一想！” 乔伊重复道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125478</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊在科学课上一直想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>回家的路上，她也一直想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140683</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有什么主意吗？” 当她们把自行车停靠在车库边上时，凯蒂问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140684</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146462</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有。” 乔伊说。她踢走了一个核桃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146463</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当全家人都坐下来吃晚饭时，乔伊还在想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天晚上，他们在吃爷爷拿手的猪排。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爸爸，你忘了洗手吗？” 凯蒂问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸低头看了看手，手很黑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是核桃污渍。” 爸爸说，“它们洗不掉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们上个星期在回收中心设立了核桃收购站。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177755</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我今天忘了戴手套。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177756</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“核桃生意怎么样？” 爷爷问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很忙！” 爸爸说，“今天雷斯从他家拿来了满满一卡车的核桃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他说他从来都没收获过这么多的核桃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191823</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今年一定会是个丰收年！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“核桃怎么了？” 凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请把猪排递给我一下！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，大家把自家土地上的核桃收集起来送到收购站。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209932</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们把核桃放进一个大机器里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209933</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它可以剥掉核桃的绿色外壳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212659</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，核桃从机器另一端出来，掉进袋子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们称重量，付核桃钱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们付多少钱？” 爷爷问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“每磅15美分。” 爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232626</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“15美分！” 爷爷说。他摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232627</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我小的时候，核桃每磅才5美分。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一年，我想买一台二手自行车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243747</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>为此，我捡了好多的核桃。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243748</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247938</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您有一个金钱目标。” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247939</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254258</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很想知道有多少孩子是用卖核桃的钱买的自行车的。” 妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254259</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁想要甜点？” 爷爷说，“我烤了一个苹果......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264811</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等等！” 乔伊说。她转头看着爸爸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264812</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269809</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁都可以捡核桃把它们卖给核桃收购站吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269810</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然。” 爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272842</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“每磅15 美分 ？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。” 爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281398</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊开心地笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281399</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285673</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们院子里有多少磅的核桃？” 她问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285674</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288733</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你觉得它们值100 美元吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288734</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293780</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸笑了。“或许吧！” 他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293781</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过，价值100 美元的核桃可不少啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>